    "name": "Skillet",
    "steam_appid": 3013040,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013040/extras/01c69a6c3a6edef158759f1a03405be8.poster.avif?t=1759174763\" width=616 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013040/extras/01c69a6c3a6edef158759f1a03405be8.webm?t=1759174763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013040/extras/01c69a6c3a6edef158759f1a03405be8.mp4?t=1759174763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skillet is a delicious arena battler where everything is flammable and bouncy. You cannot directly attack anyone but you can definitely <i>nudge</i> someone into harm's way.  Survive against friends and foes in five game modes from the comfort of your own kitchen. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built as an open-source game in Godot Engine, Skillet is completely customizable by the community and uses Steam Workshop to easily share modifications.  You can read more about it on the website.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013040/extras/0c82f4ff4c3df1544892dce840777167.poster.avif?t=1759174763\" width=616 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013040/extras/0c82f4ff4c3df1544892dce840777167.webm?t=1759174763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013040/extras/0c82f4ff4c3df1544892dce840777167.mp4?t=1759174763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The kitchen is your playground.  Be the last player standing in one of five game modes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Trial By Fire</strong><br>Avoid being ignited by various hazards while knocking friends <i>into</i> said hazards. Accidentally.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hot Potato</strong><br>The floor is lava. Well, boiling hot oil. Jump for every melting platform you can while you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pass The Torch</strong><br>The Match is &quot;it&quot; and coming for <i>you</i>. Get tagged to become yet another Match, spreading the flames.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fire-Water-Sponge</strong><br>Fire burns sponge, sponge absorbs water, water douses fire. You get how this works.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gumbo</strong><br>A little bit of everything and a boss-fight cherry on top.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013040/extras/346545c5bb7fc86010be2bfa0824cc15.poster.avif?t=1759174763\" width=616 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013040/extras/346545c5bb7fc86010be2bfa0824cc15.webm?t=1759174763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013040/extras/346545c5bb7fc86010be2bfa0824cc15.mp4?t=1759174763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock and trade a variety of skins and cosmetics with friends; even get some for just having Godot Engine in your Steam library or owning other Godot-made games like Brotato, Chillquarium, District Panic, Drift, Lila's Sky Ark, Resolutiion, Satryn Deluxe, Virtual Cottage, WindowKill, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also create your own skins and cosmetics then upload them to Steam Workshop to share with friends. Download templates from Skillet's asset repository on Github or Steam Workshop itself.</p>",
